WORK IN PROGRESS - USE WITH CAUTION - INCOMPLETE APIS

This is a simple library that will talk to Twitter in a modern way, using their XAuth APIs for
Mobile. The framework currently has no GUI. This is on purpose, it is meant as a lower level
Twitter API on which you can build any kind of application.



Initial authentication:

- (void) authenticate
{
   _twitterConsumer = [[TwitterConsumer alloc] initWithKey: @"KEY-HERE"
      secret: @"SECRET-HERE"];

   _twitterAuthenticator = [TwitterAuthenticator new];
   if (_twitterAuthenticator != nil)
   {
      _twitterAuthenticator.consumer = _twitterConsumer;
      _twitterAuthenticator.username = @"USERNAME";
      _twitterAuthenticator.password = @"PASSWORD";
      _twitterAuthenticator.delegate = self;

      [_twitterAuthenticator authenticate];
   }
}

- (void) twitterAuthenticator: (TwitterAuthenticator*) twitterAuthenticator didFailWithError: (NSError*) error;
{
   NSLog(@"TwitterAuthenticatorViewController#twitterAuthenticator: %@ didFailWithError: %@",
      twitterAuthenticator, error);
}

- (void) twitterAuthenticator: (TwitterAuthenticator*) twitterAuthenticator didSucceedWithToken: (TwitterToken*) token
{
   NSLog(@"TwitterAuthenticatorViewController#twitterAuthenticator: %@ didSucceedWithToken: %@",
      twitterAuthenticator, token);
}

Posting a tweet:

TwitterTweetPoster* tweetPoster = [TwitterTweetPoster new];
tweetPoster.consumer = _twitterConsumer;
tweetPoster.token = token;
[tweetPoster execute];
